ur entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Untitled', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'untitled', '', '', '2019-10-16 08:39:02', '2019-10-16 08:39:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/seagamefootball/source-code/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=85', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
